{
 "cells": [
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*计算Jpump，测试文件，忽略弛豫，存在自发辐射*)\r\n(*因此现在是1个激发态，两个基态，不考虑从超精细结构，激发态S1/2有两个磁量子数，基态分别是2，4，所以是8维矩阵*)\r\n(*首先写原子自能以及受激项*)\r\n(*Qm是optical spin operator Q=1/2(1e-1g)*)\r\nQm=1/2DiagonalMatrix[{1,1,-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,-1}];\r\n\r\n(*rho0，是初始密度矩阵，就是微分方程的边界，*)\r\n\r\nrho0=",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {},
   "executionSummary": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "rho0[e1_,e2_,g11_,g12_,g21_,g22_,g23_,g24_]:=DiagonalMatrix[{e1,e2,g11,g12,g21,g22,g23,g24}];\r\nrho0t[e1_,e2_,g11_,g12_,g21_,g22_,g23_,g24_]:=Exp[I*Phi[0]]*rho0[e1,e2,g11,g12,g21,g22,g23,g24]*Exp[-I*Phi[0]];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {},
   "executionSummary": {
    "timing": {
     "startTime": 1781165438510,
     "endTime": 1781165438695
    },
    "executionOrder": 1,
    "success": true
   }
  },
